title: [Caffe2] caffe2/python/caffe2_pybind11_state.so: undefined symbol: _ZN10onnx_torch11TensorProtoD1Ev
body_html:
I built caffe2 from latest pytorch source code and sudo make install sucessfully.
But I when I run "python -c 'from caffe2.python import core'" from terminal, I got:

WARNING:root:This caffe2 python run does not have GPU support. Will run in CPU only mode.
WARNING:root:Debug message: No module named caffe2_pybind11_state_hip
CRITICAL:root:Cannot load caffe2.python. Error: /home/workspace/pytorch/build/caffe2/python/caffe2_pybind11_state.so: undefined symbol: _ZN10onnx_torch11TensorProtoD1Ev

what's wrong?
